{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_01","textHome":"我家的中华料理店，从父辈开始就快倒了……@可母亲和奶奶依旧每日挥霍无度……@但是，面对这样一家子总要有人能担起责任！@那么，我，由比鹤乃！@总有一天会成为成大事立大业的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_18","textHome":"好，完成了！右腿单立保持了24小时！@好漫长啊……说来，这个训练比起消耗体力，@更像是在与无聊做斗争啊。@不过，左腿也来练一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_19","textHome":"还不够还不够还不够！……我还要变的更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_20","textHome":"嗯嗯，这样确实上了一个台阶！肯定没错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_21","textHome":"听我说呀！我就稍微练了练拳脚，@旁边的野猫就摔得四脚朝天了！@没错……肯定是我变强了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_22","textHome":"我做到啦！前阵子去动物园的时候，@我让狮子坐下了哟！就站在笼子前，@心里想着「坐下！」而已~！@我好像达到这种境界了呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_23","textHome":"嗯？新闻？「海豚秀上海豚发飙了」？@啊，确实是我！我在观众席上想着@「要是跳得再卖力点不是很帅吗？」，@它们就感觉到了！虽然我也不懂是什么原理！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_24","textHome":"哦！我等着呢！好嘞，可以走了吧！@一，二……「今天也要变强！」@喂！一起来喊啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_25","textHome":"嗯，一个激灵就醒了！@早上好！我早起超强的哦~@而且，一醒来就能精力十足哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_26","textHome":"饿了~想吃顿饭啦。@啊，我说的就是字面意义上的白米饭哦。@我最喜欢米饭啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_27","textHome":"啊——不好了不好了！得去店里帮忙了！@现在的营业额不如从前了，@要更加努力才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_03","textHome":"竟然是要和我谈心吗……没事没事！@我应该尝试各种事情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_28","textHome":"睡前必须要做的事！简而言之……自我暗示！@那么开始啦！我会变强……我会变强……@我会呼……呼……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_29","textHome":"一天的时间，发发呆就过去了！@24小时可是很短暂的哦！@要想一个不浪费时间的锻炼方法才行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_30","textHome":"由比家的命运落在我的肩上可不是在说大话，@所以我一定要变的更强！才能扛起这个家！@噗哇！忘了换气了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_31","textHome":"棒极了！就是它！这就是我想做的！@我不管是什么对手都会对战的，@来吧来吧——出来吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_32","textHome":"哇哦！燃起来了！情绪激涨！@这么大阵容的对战，哪有不嗨起来的道理！@我要去！我会超级努力的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_33","textHome":"我想出来的准备运动……取名为鹤乃体操！@开始咯？两臂举高……@然后往上顶！顶！顶100次！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_34","textHome":"我有战斗的诀窍哦，把它告诉你吧。@看着对方的眼睛，要死死盯住~@然后就发起冲锋！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_35","textHome":"中华料理是火的料理！我也总是热情似火！@虽然想做到这样，@但偶尔也会消沉到小火苗的程度……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_36","textHome":"我喜欢的一句话是「不试试怎么知道」！@船到桥头自然直就好了！@光说不练是不会有进步的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_37","textHome":"我还是喜欢直爽！最讨厌说谎和蒙骗！@所以我也总是堂堂正正地去对决！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_04","textHome":"接下来才是更加刻苦的修行，@我要成为首屈一指的魔法少女！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_38","textHome":"根据我实际较量过的印象，桃子属虎，@然后玲奈属狼的感觉。@枫？枫的话，嗯——属仓鼠？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_39","textHome":"我知道，当我沉醉于一项事物的时候@就注意不到周围了。也就是说，@我的精神很集中！对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion"